org.orgName: United States District Court For The Western District of Washington Northern Division

div1.p: TERRITORY OF WASHINGTON, County of Whitman. }ss

I, L.P. Berry, sheriff in and for said county and territory, do hereby certify that I served the within summons and annexed complaint writ and order on the within named defendant, City Marshal of Garfield W.T. Wm Isbel in Whitman County, Washington Territory, on the 1st day of Sept, A.D. 188 , by delivering to said defendant personally a copy of the summons and complaint prepared and certified to be such by the clerk of the district court, holding terms at Colfax, said county and territory.
Witness my hand, this 20th day of September, A.D. 1888 L.P. Berry Sheriff of Whitman County, W.T. By Deputy
Feb, Service of writ order Miliage
